{"tid":2450203,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖] 日本爆紅長相甜美女電單車手 真身曝光","createTime":"2021-03-17T08:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T10:14:25.000Z","uid":116696,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"36f2d8d51a4abdb3661dc8924af999b99101d758","tid":2450203,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:25:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/azusagakuyuki/status/1359307147293597701?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fazusagakuyuki%2Fstatus%2F1359307147293597701%3Fs%3D21&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=d3bd8204\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fazusagakuyuki%2Fstatus%2F1359307147293597701%3Fs%3D21&h=f7bf8b56\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/azusagakuyuki/status/1359307147293597701?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2021-03-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.28.40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2021-03-16-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.28.40.jpg&h=4e46f879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這位美女寫手的Twitter帳戶名為「宗谷的蒼冰」，她在Twiiter上亦上載了很多和電單車的合照。看上去就是一位既年輕又美麗，喜愛電單車的女性，所以吸引了不少男士粉絲，並引不少討論。<br />\n<br />\n然而，她上載的一張電單車的照片卻引起了網友們的討論。照片中電單車的後視鏡反射的是一位大叔！有人認為她是男扮女裝，有人認為該位大叔是她的父親，眾說紛紜。節目組便和當事人聯絡，並到茨城縣和真人會面！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2021-03-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.30.24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2021-03-16-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.30.24.jpg&h=98702223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他們相約在一處停車場會合。該名美女寫手一脫下電單車頭盔果真是一位大叔！！！節目組也再三確認是否本人。如此大的反差已經到了欺詐的地步了吧？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2021-03-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.31.52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2021-03-16-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.31.52.jpg&h=fbf099ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宗谷先生表示，並不是隨隨便便就能拍出如此驚為天人的照片，照明打燈是十分重要，令膚色更加顯白。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/-2021-03-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.32.30-e1615879306184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F-2021-03-16-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.32.30-e1615879306184.jpg&h=6ed1080b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2021-03-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.31.33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2021-03-16-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.31.33.jpg&h=4440e0b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他亦當場示範如何編輯照片。只是簡單利用手機的應用程式就能將一位大叔變成一位美女。他坦言，當初開設帳戶根本沒有人觀看。但用女性身份發表文章後很快得到回響，獲得1000名追隨者是十分容易的事。為了得到大家的追隨他才想出如此妙計。<br />\n<br />\n採訪最後，他跟記者分享了幾張美化前後對比的照片。我們也一起欣賞他的傑作吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2021-03-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.33.35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2021-03-16-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.33.35.jpg&h=da4350ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2021-03-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.33.46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2021-03-16-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.33.46.jpg&h=30ad3ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2021-03-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.34.17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2021-03-16-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.34.17.jpg&h=9fab6a87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57439faf2340178b2a4a6e6dd18fb45022664f80","tid":2450203,"uid":181527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"至少頭髮係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f683d868f12f0ccaa07e5580fda4950df167bf","tid":2450203,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"今朝有人post過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9544c1f879a78f6cf6eff37993f36167d3f7ada","tid":2450203,"uid":33222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:30:09.000Z","msg":"頭髮keep得幾好"},{"pid":"cb88452706a38f3ff7b1a38ceb56a01d2a01f2fd","tid":2450203,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"you竟然是個boy"},{"pid":"2bced73fc4cbf39aee79ac79ef488fe902500065","tid":2450203,"uid":259033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb88452706a38f3ff7b1a38ceb56a01d2a01f2fd","tid":2450203,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"you竟然是個bo